===Adjective===
#[[eponymous]] descriptive adjective used in [[wikipedia:Microeconomics|Microeconomics]].  Indicates the derivation of the mathematics or the effect to have come from, and be credited to, Slutsky's early twentieth century work.   
#*'''1972:''' Stanley Fischer, ''Econometrica'', v. 40, iss. 2, pp 371 - This correspondence is then used in a derivation of Slutsky equations for assets.
